data.meta_description: Monogram Pictures, Los Angeles - 1946 - Vintage studio still photograph from the 1946 film. Annotations in manuscript pencil on the verso. The second-to-last film to feature Sidney Toler as Chinese detective Charlie Chan, and the 38th of 47 "Charlie Chan" films in total. Set in San Francisco. 10 x 8 inches. Very Good, lightly age toned and edgeworn. - Shadows Over Chinatown (Original photograph from the 1946 film)
